please run the command : sh buileder.sh
to builed the TCPChat


to get the ip address of the host, run the command : "ipconfig" in the terminal and search for : 
"IPv4 Address. . . . . . . . . . . : 10.1.204.249"

10.1.204.249 is the ip in this case 

to connect to the server in the same computer use :

nc localhost $portnumber

to connect to the server in a different computer use :

nc $ipaddress $portnumber